Dialogue: 5,0:00:01.99,0:00:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Iizuka was all over Manaka-san today, trying to hold her stuff.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:05.94,0:00:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He makes it so obvious.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:07.90,0:00:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Sayu. Why's it always the same thing with you?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:12.29,0:00:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka-san?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:13.83,0:00:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:15.13,0:00:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Your face looks a little...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:17.02,0:00:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's Hikari.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:19.87,0:00:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:21.71,0:00:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hii-kun!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:27.09,0:00:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that the sea slug rock we found?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:29.55,0:00:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup. Miuna-chan made it into a necklace for me.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:32.84,0:00:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so I never lose it.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:35.10,0:00:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So you never lose it...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:43.25,0:00:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,In the five years it's been since I met you,
Dialogue: 5,0:00:45.97,0:00:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I never stopped watching you.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:49.49,0:00:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I've come to understand the sea by living beside it,
Dialogue: 5,0:00:53.84,0:00:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I've finally come to understand you{ as well}.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:57.41,0:01:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell when you'll get angry, laugh, or cry.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:04.09,0:01:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I can sense it.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:07.41,0:01:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And right now, I sense that it's me \Nyou have feelings for.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:11.79,0:01:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:25.39,0:01:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Let go of me!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:27.83,0:01:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let go if I'm wrong.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:29.47,0:01:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugu...
Dialogue: 5,0:01:31.11,0:01:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I'm not...
Dialogue: 5,0:01:36.90,0:01:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:38.40,0:01:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}are{\i0} wrong! I don't love you, Tsumugu!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:50.13,0:01:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The feelings...
Dialogue: 5,0:01:52.45,0:01:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,are everywhere.{are lingering.}{this implication is all wrong in english. instead of lingering something like float/drift is more accurate, and the implication here should be different. on the surface this is about the feelings of the sea god drifting past his vision, but of course thats merely meant to mirror their own feelings. maybe "are everywhere" would be better. the sea gods feelings still permeate the sea, and similarly feelings permeate their lives, but theyre also not constant or unchanging but go with the tides.}
