Dialogue: 5,0:14:37.29,0:14:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna do another one.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:38.98,0:14:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We're doing another Boatdrift Ceremony!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:40.70,0:14:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come give us a hand!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:47.80,0:14:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it coming!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:51.07,0:14:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:53.33,0:14:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:54.98,0:14:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Look how many people \Nhave showed up already.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:57.29,0:15:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that all this time, everyone wanted to do another Boatdrift Ceremony.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:01.10,0:15:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:02.79,0:15:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Are you—{lmao Hikari's lips aren't moving.}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:04.42,0:15:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, you really haven't aged a day, Hikari!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:07.88,0:15:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's crazy!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:09.74,0:15:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Egawa-kun?!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:11.34,0:15:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, and I brought my wife, too!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:13.43,0:15:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:14.54,0:15:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice to meet you all.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:16.56,0:15:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I contacted everyone else that left too.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:19.78,0:15:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:21.21,0:15:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:23.79,0:15:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, everyone's here!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:25.95,0:15:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sayama! Come and hold the other end!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:28.35,0:15:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like your people skills \Nhaven't improved any.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:34.21,0:15:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this sort of nostalgic?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:37.69,0:15:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you having fun too, Hii-kun?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:47.87,0:15:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How is the kimono coming along?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:53.73,0:15:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if replacing her with a Wooden Maiden like this is really going to work.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:58.55,0:16:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't know unless we try.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:00.31,0:16:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:02.31,0:16:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,During the five years I got to spend on the surface, Manaka was the sacrifice, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:11.49,0:16:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then this time, I should—
Dialogue: 5,0:16:13.96,0:16:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Chisaki!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:35.87,0:16:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, slacker.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:38.43,0:16:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:40.43,0:16:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,you like Chisaki-san.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:43.73,0:16:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Caught me red-handed, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:46.73,0:16:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:47.73,0:16:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:48.46,0:16:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,When you asked her out again, you tried to act all cool and pretend it was a joke, didn't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:54.52,0:16:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So you heard that too, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:55.86,0:16:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I did!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:57.60,0:17:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if she rejected you or what,
Dialogue: 5,0:17:00.02,0:17:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but shouldn't you be more up front about this?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:02.58,0:17:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Like...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:03.87,0:17:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,shouldn't you show her that look on your face instead of hiding it?!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:08.89,0:17:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What good would that do?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:11.69,0:17:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I showed her my feelings, she'd probably just pity me or treat me like a kid,
Dialogue: 5,0:17:16.07,0:17:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and it would be more like Akari-san comforting Hikari.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:20.25,0:17:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I could stand that.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:23.95,0:17:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I've often wondered what would have happened if I hadn't hibernated.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:29.21,0:17:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't think it would've mattered.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:31.63,0:17:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Even five years ago, \NChisaki had feelings for Tsumugu...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:35.93,0:17:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and I've always been the outsider.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:39.24,0:17:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Chisaki's eyes are always looking at someone other than me.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:42.23,0:17:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She never—
Dialogue: 5,0:17:42.96,0:17:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop acting like the tragic heroine!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:46.11,0:17:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,"Heroine"?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:47.85,0:17:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the hero?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:48.92,0:17:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just like Chisaki, you know!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:51.17,0:17:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:54.63,0:17:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This whole time...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:56.63,0:17:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been watching you.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:59.34,0:18:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:01.49,0:18:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,been looking at only you!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:03.89,0:18:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I waited for you!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:05.77,0:18:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It was all because of you.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:07.98,0:18:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I tried so hard...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:10.29,0:18:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So I could be a better person, like you...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:12.72,0:18:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So you wouldn't treat me \Nlike a little kid anymore!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:15.86,0:18:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So you would start to see me as a girl and not just a child!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:20.61,0:18:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole time you were gone,
Dialogue: 5,0:18:23.15,0:18:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,you were right here!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:25.35,0:18:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been here in my heart all this time!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:42.77,0:18:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:44.06,0:18:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:45.79,0:18:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in your heart.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:53.67,0:18:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I was actually really lonely.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:56.97,0:18:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,When I came back to the surface,
Dialogue: 5,0:18:58.96,0:19:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari had Akari-san's family,
Dialogue: 5,0:19:02.05,0:19:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and Chisaki had Tsumugu's family.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:04.89,0:19:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I really thought...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:07.01,0:19:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,there was no one who was waiting for me.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:11.27,0:19:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:12.75,0:19:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just a kid like me after all.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:14.63,0:19:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I really am.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:16.31,0:19:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you disappointed?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:17.63,0:19:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The big brother you admired is actually just a big kid.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:20.18,0:19:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go putting words in my mouth!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:23.07,0:19:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I give you a reply?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:28.53,0:19:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it already. \N"Sorry," right?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:30.49,0:19:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always been looking at Chisaki, you know.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:32.94,0:19:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know. Just stop there!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:35.23,0:19:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Sayu...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:39.19,0:19:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,from now on, I'll start looking at you.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:41.41,0:19:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Not as a child, either,
Dialogue: 5,0:19:43.66,0:19:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,but as a girl who's my age.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:48.20,0:19:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it be okay if I started there...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:51.77,0:19:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,if {\i1}we{\i0} started there?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:55.75,0:19:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty condescending, aren't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:59.57,0:20:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:00.77,0:20:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:03.33,0:20:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:10.95,0:20:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:12.95,0:20:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm about to head home.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:14.48,0:20:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:15.62,0:20:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind taking Miuna home on your way back?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:17.61,0:20:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Hop on, Miuna.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:19.61,0:20:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:20.90,0:20:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll need your help again tomorrow... or later today, actually.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:24.71,0:20:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:29.09,0:20:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:30.30,0:20:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No prob.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:41.73,0:20:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't gone home yet?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:45.06,0:20:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:46.10,0:20:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The sunrise is so pretty.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:47.60,0:20:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:51.65,0:20:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem down, Hii-kun.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:54.55,0:20:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:55.92,0:20:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that... ever since that day,
Dialogue: 5,0:20:57.94,0:21:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,so much stuff changed.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:00.03,0:21:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kinda scared it'll happen again.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:02.98,0:21:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm excited.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:04.92,0:21:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:06.45,0:21:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I don't know what might happen,
Dialogue: 5,0:21:08.50,0:21:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but right now, I get to be with everyone
Dialogue: 5,0:21:11.42,0:21:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and have lots of fun with them.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:13.87,0:21:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:15.93,0:21:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You know,
Dialogue: 5,0:21:17.61,0:21:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,there {\i1}is{\i0} someone I'm in love with.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:18.96,0:21:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:20.30,0:21:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:21.24,0:21:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:22.28,0:21:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me about it!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:23.48,0:21:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really understand that feeling...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:25.72,0:21:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:27.16,0:21:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you tell me who you love, Hii-kun?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:29.79,0:21:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Saying who you love isn't that easy.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:33.62,0:21:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:35.33,0:21:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm never going to understand, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:37.49,0:21:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you'll understand soon enough...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:39.59,0:21:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:40.82,0:21:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll know once the ceremony's over.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:42.55,0:21:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The Boatdrift Ceremony?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:45.31,0:21:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make the Boatdrift Ceremony a success.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:48.07,0:21:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna wave that flag as hard as I can.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:51.83,0:21:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The flag?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:53.61,0:21:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,'Kay!
